data.description: WATERFRONT Home just hitting the market! Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, and an exclusive half bathroom in the master suite, this residence offers both practicality and luxury. Enjoy granite counters, solid wood cabinets, and vaulted ceilings throughout. Enjoy the scenic views of the Freshwater Canal from out in your private backyard or the comfort of the Air Conditioned Florida Room. This centrally located home is just a short walk from various stores, hospitals, restaurants, and the public library. A 1-car garage adds covered parking and room for storage. Just minutes away from the brand-new Sunseeker Resort, historic downtown Punta Gorda, and the charming Fisherman’s Village – making this property a true haven for Southwest Florida living. Call today as this home will not last long!
